              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>；如果我方场上存在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">杀生樱</span>，则将其消灭，然后生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">天狐霆雷</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/56f64a44b1ccee62527e2a18a46de27f_4205061397262402690.png",
