                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "大密法 · 天狐显真"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到6次）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方宣布结束时：</span>如果此牌的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>至少为4，则造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。（需消耗<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7162703718417125962.png",
                "id": "talent91116",
                "key": "杀生樱",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/9935fc2ef27a255d96756090578adee7_172899435957518348.png",
                "title": "杀生樱"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8417579295666089533.png",
